which I have to say, Pam,

540
00:17:16,677 --> 00:17:18,026
is a very tough stance to take.

541
00:17:18,069 --> 00:17:19,114
- I don't want to blow up,

542
00:17:19,157 --> 00:17:21,421
but the man said
he'd give me $500,000.

543
00:17:21,464 --> 00:17:24,119
This is so Bobby can take care
of my granddaughter.

544
00:17:24,162 --> 00:17:26,034
That girl means the world
to me.

545
00:17:26,077 --> 00:17:27,078
- Fine, fine.
Point to Pam.

546
00:17:27,122 --> 00:17:28,602
But if you care about her
so much,

547
00:17:28,645 --> 00:17:29,733
how can you just
blow yourself up?

548
00:17:29,777 --> 00:17:30,734
You'll never get to see her
again.

549
00:17:30,778 --> 00:17:31,909
- Well, at least I know

550
00:17:31,953 --> 00:17:33,563
she'll be financially
well taken care of.

551
00:17:33,607 --> 00:17:36,610
- Sure, but is this really how
you want her to remember you?

552
00:17:36,653 --> 00:17:38,176
As a murderer?
- I'd rather be remembered

553
00:17:38,220 --> 00:17:40,701
