but it's not.

577
00:18:21,045 --> 00:18:23,657
There's still one end
of this bowel that's open.

578
00:18:23,700 --> 00:18:25,833
- Which end?

579
00:18:25,876 --> 00:18:29,271
- The butt end.
- I'm listening.

580
00:18:29,314 --> 00:18:31,534
- Okay, if you hand me
that bomb right now,

581
00:18:31,578 --> 00:18:34,755
